title: The Fly Trap
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, International, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A diner that offers some vegetarian and vegan suitable dishes. Example: veggie rumble (tofu, veggies, spinach, omit provolone cheese); pea patch sandwich (eggplant, mushroom, carrot, peppers, and tomato on wheat, omit provolone), tempting tempeh burger (omit mayonnaise), fried rice (brown rice, veggies, tofu), and the house salad.
